dia.com.hk/articles/2017/06/17/162225\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.vjmedia.com.hk%2Farticles%2F2017%2F06%2F17%2F162225&d=dqKSpZxk9nt8wP7CWeVsBYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=62393026\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2017/06/17/162225</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年3月22日，立法會審議 1131億臨時撥款，在全體泛民議員缺席下，議案只花兩分鐘，由不足十名建制派議員在不記名投票下贊成通過。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180322/bkn-20180322090338992-0322_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180322%2Fbkn-20180322090338992-0322_00822_001.html&d=dqKSpZxk9nt8wP7CWeVsBYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=375d7ffd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180322/bkn-20180322090338992-0322_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年5月26日，工務小組審議17.85億元朗行人天橋撥款，議案以3票之差獲得通過，5名泛民議員缺席未有投票。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/fc/pwsc/results/v201805261.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr17-18%2Fchinese%2Ffc%2Fpwsc%2Fresults%2Fv201805261.pdf&d=dqKSpZxk9nt8wP7CWeVsBYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=5bb4d70c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/fc/pwsc/results/v201805261.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年5月25日，林卓廷提出就「升降機維修保養對市民安全進行辯論議案」以6票之差未獲通過，7名泛民議員缺席未有投票。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/hc/voting/hc20180525-voting-ec.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr17-18%2Fchinese%2Fhc%2Fvoting%2Fhc20180525-voting-ec.pdf&d=dqKSpZxk9nt8wP7CWeVsBYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=03177f1b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/hc/voting/hc20180525-voting-ec.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年5月31日，建制派「共建粵港澳大灣區」動議順利通過，地方選區輸2票，2名泛民議員缺席未有投票。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/counmtg/voting/v20180530.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr17-18%2Fchinese%2Fcounmtg%2Fvoting%2Fv20180530.pdf&d=dqKSpZxk9nt8wP7CWeVsBYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=90d3d03f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/counmtg/voting/v20180530.pdf</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T12:46:29.000Z","msg":"立法會飯民再次反勝為敗：許智峰尹兆堅胡志偉缺席投票，民主黨公民黨莫乃光8票倒戈贊成通過工務小組48億元撥款興建第三跑設施<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/800/1*Gj07iRC1Vxp97i78SJ-ndA.jpeg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn-images-1.medium.com%2Fmax%2F800%2F1%2AGj07iRC1Vxp97i78SJ-ndA.jpeg&d=dqKSpZxk9nt8wP7CWeVsBYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=518872df\" target=\"_blank\">https://cdn-images-1.medium.com/max/800/1*Gj07iRC1Vxp97i78SJ-ndA.jpeg</a>"},{"pid":"ea3dc783b849932269d24e21ac153ed9955a25ce","tid":916822,"uid":52230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T12:56:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb956f4467ecf10314bf026d5cb158b8e3f99a86","tid":916822,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd03b571633aa1c27577f0ab16cef7427ff2de43","tid":916822,"uid":48234,"like":11,"dislike":26,"score":-15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T03:32:24.000Z","msg":"港豬: 沒有民主中國哪有民主香港"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T13:00:36.000Z","msg":"卓人:我幾時講過要等中國有民主<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0FxvMpv5mr0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D0FxvMpv5mr0&d=dqKSpZxk9nt8wP7CWeVsBYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=a401dfa3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0FxvMpv5mr0</a>"},{"pid":"89b74facdcc33e49daf424f71875f44fca08cab0","tid":916822,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T13:06:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd6e6b22f82fc6befa83b88b2d99c10b93da7ce0","tid":91682